✨ Overview
AlphaForge AI is an Agentic AI Financial Research Platform built using FastAPI, Groq LLM, LangChain, ChromaDB (RAG), yFinance, and NewsAPI.
Instead of a single chatbot, AlphaForge uses multiple specialized AI agents coordinated by a Report Agent to produce comprehensive investment-grade research.
---
🧠 Agentic Architecture
```text
                    User
                      │
                      ▼
               FastAPI Backend
                      │
                      ▼
              Report Agent (Brain)
      ┌──────────┼──────────┬─────────┐
      ▼          ▼          ▼         ▼
 Financial     News     Competitor   Charts
   Agent       Agent      Agent      Agent
      │          │          │         │
      └──────────┼──────────┴─────────┘
                 ▼
              Groq LLM
                 ▼
         AI Research Report
```
🔥 Core Features
🚀 Feature	Description
📈 Financial Agent	Revenue, EPS, ROE, PE Ratio, Cash Flow, Debt
📰 News Agent	Fetches and summarizes latest news
🏆 Competitor Agent	AI-powered competitor benchmarking
📊 Chart Agent	Revenue, EBITDA, Stock Trends
📄 Report Agent	Generates complete investment report
🧠 RAG	Context-aware retrieval using ChromaDB
🛠 Tech Stack
Layer	Technologies
Backend	FastAPI, Python
AI	Groq LLM, LangChain
RAG	ChromaDB
Financial Data	yFinance
News	NewsAPI
Validation	Pydantic
Server	Uvicorn
📂 Project Structure
```text
backend/
├── agents/
│   ├── financial_agent.py
│   ├── news_agent.py
│   ├── competitor_agent.py
│   ├── chart_agent.py
│   └── report_agent.py
├── services/
├── rag/
├── chroma_db/
├── routers/
└── main.py
```
⚙️ Installation
```bash
git clone <repo-url>
cd AlphaForge
python -m venv venv
```
Windows
```bash
venv\Scripts\activate
```
Install
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```
Run
```bash
uvicorn main:app --reload
```
Open:
`http://localhost:8000/docs`
📡 API
Endpoint	Purpose
`/financial/{ticker}`	Financial analysis
`/news/{ticker}`	News insights
`/compare/{ticker}`	Competitor comparison
`/charts/{ticker}`	Financial charts
`/report/{ticker}`	Final AI report
